=Content: {{ $('OpenAI').item.json.text }}

Known workers (use EXACT spelling from this list when matching): {{ $('Fetch Static Lists').first().json.worker_names_list }}
Known areas (use EXACT spelling from this list when matching): {{ $('Fetch Static Lists').first().json.area_names_and_aliases_list }}
Known clients (use EXACT spelling from this list when matching): {{ $('Fetch Static Lists').first().json.client_names_list }}
Known work types (use EXACT name from this list): {{ $('Fetch Static Lists').first().json.work_types_list }}
Known materials (prefer names from this list, but if the speaker mentions a material not on the list, still extract the name as-is): {{ $('Fetch Static Lists').first().json.materials_list }}

IMPORTANT: Whisper often misrecognizes Hebrew names. Apply phonetic correction before matching.
For each extracted name, if it sounds like a known worker/area/client (within 1-2 consonant differences), output the known spelling.
If a name is not on the list and no phonetic match exists, output it as-is — do not discard.

